                            <comment id="12841734" author="ryanobjc" created="Fri, 5 Mar 2010 07:32:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;we might be able to use this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mvn dependency:build-classpath&lt;/p&gt;

